Module kline.qkmii.inventorymgmtsystem

module kline.qkmii.inventorymgmtsystem
This module provides all the packages for an inventory management system with JavaFX. Packages are structured with the MVC framework.

The kline.qkmii.inventorymgmtsystem contains the main application and JavaFX FXML loading and dialog creation.

The kline.qkmii.inventorymgmtsystem.controller contains controller classes for the views and access to the models.

The kline.qkmii.inventorymgmtsystem.controller.parts contains the controllers for the parts form view.

The kline.qkmii.inventorymgmtsystem.controller.products contains the controllers for the products form view.

The kline.qkmii.inventorymgmtsystem.model contains the model classes that handle logic and the database.

The kline.qkmii.inventorymgmtsystem.util contains extra tools that are used throughout the application.

Author:
Timothy Albert Kline
